results.p: Rapid CRC Unicode allows you to create and verify CRC, MD5, and SHA hashes within the files themselves or within sfv/md5/sha1/sha256/sha512 files.
RapidCRC is an open source CRC/MD5/SHA hashing program. I've extended the current unicode support to allow writing of unicode .sfv/.md5/.sha1/.sha256/.sha512 ...
